2. IMPRESSIONIST MASTERWORKS IN BOSTON

Boston, MA
March 9, 2002
$200 per person
200 packages available
Max.: 8 per Card member
On Sale: Nov. 30, 2 pm ET

Discover more than 75 Impressionist masterworks during an exclusive
viewing of "Impressionist Still Life" at the Museum of Fine Arts,
Boston. While the museum is closed to the public, you'll have the
rare private opportunity to see still-life masterpieces by Monet,
Van Gogh, Cezanne, Degas, and more. You'll also enjoy a cocktail
reception and lecture and take home the exhibition catalog.

To make reservations, please call 800-321-RSVP. For information
about additional By Invitation Only events, visit:
http://tm0.com/americanexpress/sbct.cgi?s=65181741&i=420518&d=2031525


