4. GIFT GIVING MADE EASY WITH PLATINUM CONCIERGE

For many people, finding the perfect gift is the best part of
the holidays. Now, the Gift Specialists at Platinum Concierge
can help make choosing gifts easier and more enjoyable than ever.
This handpicked team of specialists has vast knowledge in the
gift-giving arena, and is on call to consult and assist you with
all of your gift-giving needs.

Let Platinum Concierge help you make this holiday season extra
special for all those on your shopping list. Gift Specialists are
available by phone at 800-345-AMEX from 9 a.m. to 9 p.m. EST
Monday through Friday.


